# Dataverse Backend

- Dev Dataverse URL: `https://dev-itt-apps.crm8.dynamics.com`
- Invoice display name: Invoice Details
- EntitySetName: `dia_invoicedetailses`
- Primary key: `dia_invoicedetailsid`

## Key columns

| Column | Use |
|--------|-----|
| `dia_status` | Status — plain TEXT (not choice) |
| `dia_invoicedate` | Invoice Date — all period filters |
| `dia_invoicenumber` | Auto after submit |
| `dia_ponumber` | PO Number |
| `dia_AccountID` | Partner lookup |
| `dia_ProjectID` | Project lookup |
| `dia_ServiceStartDate` / `dia_ServiceEndDate` | Service period |
| `dia_isReported` | Failure reported (`Yes` or blank) |
| `dia_InternalNotes` | Rich text |
| `dia_AdhocInvoice` | Yes/No |

## Related tables (Create Invoice)

| Table | EntitySetName | Notes |
|-------|---------------|-------|
| Account (Partner) | `accounts` | Partner dropdown |
| Project | `dia_projects` | LogicalName `dia_project`; Region `ittdev_region`; Partner lookup `ittdev_account`; Name `dia_projectname`; Status Active |
| Contract | `ittdev_contracts` | Lookup `ittdev_dia_Project` → Project; `ittdev_startdate` / `ittdev_enddate`; `statecode` Active; Name `ittdev_name` |
| Product/Services | `dia_productserviceses` | Name `dia_productservicename`; Rate `dia_productservicerate`; Type `ittdev_productservicetype` (Editable Rate / Non-Editable Rate / Discount) |
| Billing Info (line items) | `dia_invoicelineitemdetailses` | Qty `dia_quantity`; Rate `dia_rate`; Total `dia_total`; Invoice lookup `dia_invoiceid` |
| Invoice Filtering Options | `dia_invoicefilteringoptionses` | This Month / Last Month windows for duplicate checks |
| Security Roles | `dia_securityroles` | Admin elevation |

## Status values

`Draft, Submitted, Reviewed, Approved, Flagged, Cancelled, Sent,
Fail-Creation, Fail-Update, Fail-Flag, Fail-Approval, Fail-Review`

**Failed (Dashboard)** = all five `Fail-*` **and** `dia_isReported` blank.

## Billing cycle date filter

```
dia_invoicedate ge {6th current month ISO} and dia_invoicedate le {5th next month ISO}
```

Use `getBillingCycleDates()` — not calendar month. Period variants: see `50-app-functionality`.

## Count query pattern

```
GET {DATAVERSE_URL}/api/data/v9.2/dia_invoicedetailses
  ?$filter=({status}) and ({date})
  &$count=true &$top=1 &$select=dia_invoicedetailsid
```

Headers: `Authorization: Bearer {token}`, OData 4.0, `Prefer: odata.include-annotations="*"`.
Read total from `@odata.count`.

Example Failed filter:

```
(dia_status eq 'Fail-Creation' or ... or dia_status eq 'Fail-Review')
and (dia_isReported eq null or dia_isReported eq '')
```

## Token capture

Intercept Canvas traffic: `page.on('request')` for `crm8.dynamics.com` with
`Authorization: Bearer`. Capture in `test.beforeAll` once per describe. Type the
callback param as `Request` from `@playwright/test`.

```ts
const onRequest = (req: Request) => {
  const authHeader = req.headers()['authorization'];
  if (req.url().includes('crm8.dynamics.com') && authHeader?.startsWith('Bearer ')) {
    page.off('request', onRequest);
    resolve(authHeader.replace('Bearer ', ''));
  }
};
page.on('request', onRequest);
```
